From 2eb2d91b631397c00c2510f5ebb463abf516c171 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Thu, 2 Jul 2026 13:43:32 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Nomenclature these + figures Pareto + note ultime +
 confirmation 0.90

Renommage des strategies (mapping consigne dans READMEs et notes) :
  RB2(SoH_bat) = plafond SoC vieillissant seul (ex RB2(SoCmax)/socwin)
  RB2(SoH_H2)  = setpoints H2 x SoH_fc/SoH_ely (ex RB2(SoH))
  RB2(SoH_all) = les deux leviers etat de sante (ex "unifiee")
  RB2(SoH_all+Pred) = strategie ultime (ex RB2 ULTIME) ; dossier renomme.

- Figures Pareto (nouvelles nomenclatures, 2 versions avec/sans isocouts) :
  Fable/pareto_ems_fable*      : RB2, RB2(SoH_bat), RB2(SoH_H2), RB2(SoH_all)
  Fable_pred/pareto_ems_ultime*: + RB2(Pred) (impact pur de la prevision sur
  RB2 nu, 2.5312/58.962 N=200) et RB2(SoH_all+Pred) (2.9421/53.095).
- Fable_pred/note_rb2_ultime.txt : note manuscrit (77.10-77.22, decomposition
  en cascade, interaction plafond x pre-charge, plateaux omni) + nomenclature.
- bench_ultime.py : labels renommes + ligne "RB2(SoH_all+Pred) (0.90)" pour
  confirmer a N=200 la config retenue par le sweep target (77.103 a N=64).

Co-Authored-By: Claude Fable 5 <noreply@anthropic.com>
Claude-Session: https://claude.ai/code/session_01S5DnMhbYaVGE7pYKS9b37j
